1993;;Younger and Younger;;American;;Percy Adlon;;Donald Sutherland, Brendan Fraser, Lolita Davidovich;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Younger_and_Younger;;Jonathan Younger owns a self-storage facility. He has a strained relationship with wife Penny, a plain and skittish woman who is startled by a noise Jonathan makes and dies from a heart attack.<br><br>Jonathan's college-aged son Winston returns home to help run the family business. While they interact with a number of quirky customers, Jonathan is haunted by the spirit of his late wife, who becomes increasingly attractive to him with each ghostly apparition.